  pygtksourceview-2.0.0-r1.ebuild, pygtksourceview-2.2.0.ebuild,
  pygtksourceview-2.4.0.ebuild:
  Add python_need_rebuild per bug #244610.

  13 Nov 2008; Brent Baude <ranger@gentoo.org> pygtksourceview-2.2.0.ebuild:
  Marking pygtksourceview-2.2.0 ppc64 stable for bug 236971

*pygtksourceview-2.4.0 (19 Oct 2008)

  19 Oct 2008; Gilles Dartiguelongue <eva@gentoo.org>
  +pygtksourceview-2.4.0.ebuild:
  New version for GNOME 2.24. Drop gnome-vfs dependency and requires new
  gtksourceview-2.3.

  25 Sep 2008; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> pygtksourceview-2.2.0.ebuild:
  Stable for HPPA (bug #236971).

  12 Aug 2008; Raúl Porcel <armin76@gentoo.org>
  pygtksourceview-2.2.0.ebuild:
  alpha/ia64/sparc stable wrt #229709

  10 Aug 2008; Markus Meier <maekke@gentoo.org>
  pygtksourceview-2.2.0.ebuild:
  x86 stable, bug #229709

  30 Jul 2008; Brent Baude <ranger@gentoo.org> pygtksourceview-2.2.0.ebuild:
  Marking pygtksourceview-2.2.0 ppc stable for bug 229709

  26 Jul 2008; Olivier Crête <tester@gentoo.org>
  pygtksourceview-2.2.0.ebuild:
